{"title":"Python 字符串操作","uid":"a6cc85e12f76b1f87c9f343cdd3617c3","slug":"Pyhon/Python 字符串操作","date":"2022-08-15T07:00:00.000Z","updated":"2023-08-19T06:41:45.350Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Pyhon/Python 字符串操作.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/img/python/logo.png","content":"<h2 id=\"字符串的创建\">1. 字符串的创建</h2>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">var1 &#x3D; &#39;hello&#39;\nvar2 &#x3D; &#39;world&#39;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"python-访问字符串中的值\">2. Python 访问字符串中的值</h2>\n<p>python中使用切片来截取字符串其中一段内容，切片截取的内容不包含结束下标对应的数据</p>\n<p>[起始下标 : 结束下标 : 步长]</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">var &#x3D; &#39;helloworld&#39;\nstr &#x3D; var[0:2]\nprint(str)\n&#39;&#39;&#39;\nhe\n&#39;&#39;&#39;</code></pre>\n<p>从后向前索引</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">var &#x3D; &#39;helloworld&#39;\nstr &#x3D; var[-4:-2]\nprint(str)\n&#39;&#39;&#39;\nor\n&#39;&#39;&#39;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"循环输出\">3. 循环输出</h2>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">str &#x3D; &#39;ab def&#39;\nfor i in str:\n    print(i)\n&#39;&#39;&#39;\na\nb\n\nd\ne\nf\n&#39;&#39;&#39;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"统计出现的次数\">4. 统计出现的次数</h2>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">str &#x3D; &#39;ab def&#39;\nprint(str.count(&#39;a&#39;))\n&#39;&#39;&#39;\n1\n&#39;&#39;&#39;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"元素以指定的字符连接生成一个新的字符串\">5. 元素以指定的字符连接生成一个新的字符串</h2>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">str &#x3D; &#39;ab def&#39;\nprint(&#39;-&#39;.join(str))\n&#39;&#39;&#39;\na-b- -d-e-f-\n&#39;&#39;&#39;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"去除左空格\">6. 去除左空格</h2>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">str &#x3D; &#39;ab def&#39;\nprint(str.lstrip())\n&#39;&#39;&#39;\nab def\n&#39;&#39;&#39;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"去除右空格\">7. 去除右空格</h2>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">str &#x3D; &#39; ab def &#39;\nprint(str.rstrip())\n&#39;&#39;&#39;\n ab def\n &#39;&#39;&#39;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"去除两边空格\">8. 去除两边空格</h2>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">str &#x3D; &#39; ab def &#39;\nprint(str.strip())\n&#39;&#39;&#39;\nab def\n&#39;&#39;&#39;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"判断目标字符是否存在\">9. 判断目标字符是否存在</h2>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">str &#x3D; &#39; ab def &#39;\nprint(str.find(&#39;c&#39;))\nprint(str.find(&#39;d&#39;))\n&#39;&#39;&#39;\n-1\n4\n&#39;&#39;&#39;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"检查目标字符索引\">10. 检查目标字符索引</h2>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">str &#x3D; &#39; ab def&#39;\nprint(str.index(&#39;b&#39;))\n&#39;&#39;&#39;\n2\n&#39;&#39;&#39;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"判断字符串是否以固定字符开始\">11. 判断字符串是否以固定字符开始</h2>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">str &#x3D; &#39;Hello World&#39;\nprint(str.startswith(&#39;h&#39;))\nprint(str.startswith(&#39;H&#39;))\n&#39;&#39;&#39;\nFalse\nTrue\n&#39;&#39;&#39;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"判断字符串是否以固定字符结尾\">12. 判断字符串是否以固定字符结尾</h2>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">str &#x3D; &#39;Hello World&#39;\nprint(str.endswith(&#39;D&#39;))\nprint(str.endswith(&#39;d&#39;))\n&#39;&#39;&#39;\nFalse\nTrue\n&#39;&#39;&#39;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"首字母转换为大写\">13. 首字母转换为大写</h2>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">str &#x3D; &#39;helloworld&#39;\nprint(str.capitalize())\n&#39;&#39;&#39;\nHelloworld\n&#39;&#39;&#39;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"转大写\">14. 转大写</h2>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">str &#x3D; &#39;Hello World&#39;\nprint(str.upper())\n&#39;&#39;&#39;\nHELLO WORLD\n&#39;&#39;&#39;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"转小写\">15. 转小写</h2>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">str &#x3D; &#39;Hello World&#39;\nprint(str.lower())\n&#39;&#39;&#39;\nhello world\n&#39;&#39;&#39;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"首字母转大写\">16. 首字母转大写</h2>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">str &#x3D; &#39;hello world&#39;\nprint(str.title())\n&#39;&#39;&#39;\nHello World\n&#39;&#39;&#39;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"大写变小写小写变大写\">17. 大写变小写，小写变大写</h2>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">str &#x3D; &#39;Hello World&#39;\nprint(str.swapcase())\n&#39;&#39;&#39;\nhELLO wORLD\n&#39;&#39;&#39;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"分割字符串\">18. 分割字符串</h2>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">str &#x3D; &#39;Hello World&#39;\nprint(str.split(&#39; &#39;))\n# [&#39;Hello&#39;, &#39;World&#39;]</code></pre>\n","text":"1. 字符串的创建 var1 &#x3D; &#39;hello&#39; var2 &#x3D; &#39;world&#39; 2. Python 访问字符串中的值 python中使用切片来截取字符串其中一段内容，切片截取的内容不包含结束下标对应的数据 [起始下标 : 结束下...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.2k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Python","slug":"Python","count":5,"path":"api/categories/Python.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Python tips","slug":"Python-tips","count":5,"path":"api/tags/Python-tips.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%E7%9A%84%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1. 字符串的创建</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#python-%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%